AsciiDoc TextMate bundle
========================

This is a TextMate bundle for AsciiDoc, see http://www.methods.co.nz/asciidoc/

It's got some basic commands and snippets working. The language grammar is a mess and not really doing anything useful right now.

Commands and Snippets
---------------------

Commands:

 - Preview
 - Convert Document
 - Typeset as PDF
 - Show Documentation

Snippets:

 - Bold
 - Italic
 - Quoted
 - Superscript
 - Subscript

Installation
------------

To install via Git:

    cd ~/"Library/Application Support/TextMate/Bundles/"
    git clone git://github.com/zuckschwerdt/asciidoc.tmbundle.git "AsciiDoc.tmbundle"
    osascript -e 'tell app "TextMate" to reload bundles'

Source can be viewed or forked via GitHub: http://github.com/zuckschwerdt/asciidoc.tmbundle/tree/master

